Wow I’m 30 years old, my birthday was on June 8th and here’s a recap of my weekend. 

Reflection Time:

Last year was definitely a journey for me. Navigating through this thing we call LIFE is a crazy roller coaster ride. Staying on course with your end goal in mind can take a mental toll on you when life throws so many obstacles your way. As I was dealing with so much mentally, a quote from my Dad kept me going. “Be like a palm tree through life’s storms, no matter how fast the winds blow, and how much the palm tree bends. The PALM TREE never breaks, it always finds a way to straighten back up. “ 

I embrace my 30s and welcome more discipline, love, health wealth, and abundance. #dirty30 #30thbirthday #birthdayweekend #dubai #dubailife
